title: The Bots Master
description:
I was cleaning out my old Videotape collection a while back and found three video tapes with 'The Bots Master' written on the label. Since I had been personally looking for these for a while with no luck (with the exception of the low quality YouTube rips), I immediately stuck these in my VCR-DVD recorder for transfer to DVD and encoding on PC.

These were recorded from the Australian Channel 7's breakfast TV show 'The Big Breakfast' in late 1999/early 2000. This show not only added the local time in the corner of the screen, but enclosed it with their own 'Big Breakfast' logo which also occasionally showed the weather for the day in each Australian city. Thankfully, it's not too intrusive however.

I make no guarantee of the quality of these episodes, I have simply posted them here since I know many people have been looking for this series. I personally think however that the picture quality is somewhat better than the YouTube rips and has a higher resolution.

Unfortunately I do not have all 40 episodes, what I have is episode 1-8 and 10-33. Other than any opening/end credits missing, I have made some notes next to the episode list below of any issues with any of the episodes.
